<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.2">
<l>pattu nīḷmuṭi yumavaṟ ṟiraṭṭip pāḻit tōḷumpa ṭaittavaṉ celvam,</l>
<l>cittam maṅkaiyar pālvaittuk keṭṭāṉ ceyva toṉṟaṟi yāvaṭi yōṅkaḷ</l>
<l>otta tōḷiraṇ ṭumoru muṭiyu moruvar tamtiṟat tōmaṉṟi vāḻntōm</l>
<l>atta vemperu māṉemmaik kollē lañci ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We servants, who did not know anything of what the one who was ruined did,</l>
<l rend="indent">placing his wealth and mind on women,</l>
<l>The one who acquired ten tall crowns and double that of broad shoulders,</l>
<l>We lived without being allies of the one with two equal arms and one head.</l>
<l>Father, our lord, do not slay us. We are frightened.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
